{"tid":107484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"懷舊撚，一人一個細個士多會賣嘅嘢。","createTime":"2017-02-04T13:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T13:55:15.000Z","uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ef4866fa629ab60411481a44bf6f3a79fc7d0b","tid":107484,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:45:10.000Z","msg":"拋磚先<br />\n超人魷魚絲，唔係因為鍾意食，而係因為裡面嘅超人徽章然後攞黎同朋友係台上鬥彈，輸咗就充公俾對方。以前有成堆徽章最後俾小學班主任收曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗食嘅之外，士多有嘅嘢都可以講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681ee911707b077e2c524809da2f8fefc00b5e91","tid":107484,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:47:01.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5bd5ea060bf74481167b38509f54ee4bd3cc3f38","tid":107484,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:47:11.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"b21d2317be071bb0af7d33e46f0a200fcf703f54","tid":107484,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:47:21.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"41c708326a3a294f241496aa1bb95ae7d791057a","tid":107484,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:47:31.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"d1e44c50d560caa9f2c4e79e28dc21818f470fc6","tid":107484,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:47:42.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"9e66ba17c48790ffe9637dd49897983c4ff3f8f7","tid":107484,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:47:52.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"3867d942d02c262efad4db081c15087a382a3c53","tid":107484,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"456a536e9a67709ce377ff21caef47a21fbb73bf","tid":107484,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:48:13.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"78381f1aa723a3ac6bd0176f3f48befa2fbaf181","tid":107484,"uid"